title: What We've Learned This Season, Part I
description:
Former FBI agent and criminal profiler Candice DeLong is joined by her producer, Julie, to discuss the episodes of season one: what they've learned, what they've missed, which murders affected them the most, and what it's like to live and breathe a true crime podcast.
